Subject: Re: Privacy Request
Importance: High

Kia ora, Tower team, I=E2=80=99m hoping you can help me straighten somethin=
g out. Back on 1 July 2025 I asked for a full copy of my claim files for C9=
0306048 and C90306256. Since then, I=E2=80=99ve received a couple of broken=
 ShareFile links and, only just

Kia ora, Tower team,
I=E2=80=99m hoping you can help me straighten something out. Back on 1 July=
 2025 I asked for a full copy of my claim files for C90306048 and C90306256=
. Since then, I=E2=80=99ve received a couple of broken ShareFile links and,=
 only just now, a working link with a small bundle of six documents.
I may be misunderstanding, but I expected a broader set of records. A few t=
hings have left me unsure:

  *   Mixed folders =E2=80=93 Once I finally received a working link, it sh=
owed both a folder with my name and another customer=E2=80=99s name. I=E2=
=80=99m not sure whether that was intentional or a display error, but it ma=
de me nervous that I might be seeing things I shouldn=E2=80=99t=E2=80=94or =
that others could see mine (see attached screenshot). It seems to be a secu=
rity and privacy issue. Could you please confirm (a) what occurred, (b) wha=
t records were exposed, (c) the containment steps taken. Also I believe you=
 might have make a notifiable privacy breach report to the Office of the Pr=
ivacy Commissioner and notify the impacted individuals as required
  *   Scope/quantity =E2=80=93 The six documents look like only a tiny part=
 of the total timeline and scope. I was expecting, to cover the full period=
 not just the very beginning and I was expecting the full claim diary/notes=
, internal emails, instructions to contractors, quotes/scopes/variations, s=
ite photos/videos, test results (e.g., moisture/soot/asbestos), call record=
ings/transcripts, texts, messages, any engineering or builder assessments, =
and third=E2=80=91party correspondence
  *   Redactions =E2=80=93 A lot of blacking=E2=80=91out appears to cover m=
ore than just other people=E2=80=99s names/contact details. If there are pa=
rts you really do need to withhold, could you please provide a short note e=
xplaining the reason for each redaction?
Could you help me with the following so I can get back on track?

  *   Full file (securely): Please resend the complete claim files for both=
 claims via a secure method (encrypted link or hard copy).
  *   Simple document index: A single list of everything held on the file (=
date, author, short description) so I can confirm I=E2=80=99ve received the=
 lot.
  *   Redaction reasons: Where something truly can=E2=80=99t be provided, a=
 short reason and, if possible, a partially released copy with only the sen=
sitive bits removed.
  *   ShareFile clarity: Confirmation of (a) what occurred, (b) what record=
s were exposed, (c) containment steps taken, and (d) confirmation that a no=
tifiable privacy breach report has been made to the Office of the Privacy C=
ommissioner and impacted individuals notified, with the reference number or=
 clarification why this was not done
  *   Call recordings/transcripts & communications: Please include any call=
 recordings or transcripts, text/SMS or instant messages, video calls, any =
other forms of communication, and notes from face=E2=80=91to=E2=80=91face m=
eetings.
Given I asked for my full file on 1 July 2025 and again on 28 August 2025, =
and I still haven=E2=80=99t received the complete material =E2=80=93 just a=
 very tiny part - could you please share the full files immediately?
Important housekeeping: I=E2=80=99d be grateful if you could please preserv=
e all claim records (including emails, texts, photos, task logs, and any co=
ntractor files) while this is sorted.
Thank you very much for helping me get clarity. I really appreciate it.
Ng=C4=81 mihi,
Raffaella Del Prete

